Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:05:00.37,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(191,502)\fad(0,80)\bord0.5\fs34}迪亚娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:05:00.37,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(285,656)\fad(0,80)\fs30}勉强抵消SLB-MR
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:04:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算是幸存下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下来的除了我…还有两个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在向我靠近  这个速度是昴？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:12.50,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\pos(953,505)\bord0.5}薇薇欧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答错了  是我薇薇欧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧？为什么几乎毫发无损？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:19.89,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(227,92)\fad(0,80)\bord0.5\fs34}昴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:19.89,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(339,294)\fad(0,80)\fs30}从SLB-PS下保护薇薇欧  无法行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吧  这就是特救魂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:22.81,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(834,479)\fad(80,0)\bord0.5\fs34}诺威
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:22.81,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(942,680)\fad(80,0)\fs30}SLB命中后被薇薇欧攻击击落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪亚娜小姐  我要过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是别过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霸王…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空破断（暂定）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:47.96,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,80)\pos(241,517)\bord0.5}爱因哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇欧同学  我不会让你靠近迪亚娜小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  爱因哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那下就已经被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇欧向迪亚娜发射了什么对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(755,646)\fs36}Sonic Shooter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  单发的音速射手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇欧同学  好像就剩我们两个了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我要上了  爱因哈特同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆对手的攻击并做出对策的学习能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快速而精密的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惧怕对手攻击  反而挺身出拳的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的战斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是防守反击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这  一闪必中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Accel Smash
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅疾破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:52.15,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(241,89)\fad(80,0)\bord0.5\fs30}薇薇欧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:52.15,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(241,250)\fad(80,0)\fs30}击落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:52.15,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1043,522)\fad(80,0)\bord0.5\fs30}爱因哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:52.15,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1043,683)\fad(80,0)\fs30}击落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:07:00.57,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(472,200)\fad(0,1000)\1cFFFFFF\3cB99826\fs25}蓝队
